=== NFL records ===
Manning holds a number of individual career records:

==== Regular season ====
* Highest passer rating, season: 121.1 (2004)<ref name="NFLRecordsBook">{{cite web|url=http://www.nfl.com/history/randf/records/indiv/passing|title=NFL Records Book&nbsp;<U+2013> Passing Records|publisher=NFL.com|accessdate=2007-01-14}}</ref>
