* Most consecutive seasons with at least 4,000 passing yards: 6 (1999<U+2013>2004)<ref name="YDSleader" />
* Most consecutive seasons with at least 20 touchdown passes: 13 (1998<U+2013>2010; current) <ref name="coltsbio" />
* Most consecutive seasons with at least 25 touchdown passes: 12 (1998<U+2013>2009; current)<ref name="yahoo.com sports" />
