==== Position on passing statistics leaderboards ====
Manning is currently on pace to break the career records in every major statistical category for a quarterback, including most career passing touchdowns, most career completions, and most career passing yards.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indystar.com/apps/pbcs.dll/section?Category=SPORTS0301|title=Indy Star&nbsp;<U+2013> Manning Meter|work=The Indianapolis Star|accessdate=2007-12-21}}</ref> Manning is currently ranked in the top four in all of these categories:
* [[List of National Football League passing touchdowns leaders|Touchdown Passes]]: 386 (3rd)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pro-football-reference.com/leaders/pass_td_career.htm|title=Pro Football Reference&nbsp;<U+2013> Career Passing Touchdowns Leaders|publisher=pro-football-reference.com|author=Drinen, Doug|accessdate=2007-12-21}}</ref>
* [[List of National Football League passing completions leaders|Passes Completed]]: 4,518 (3rd)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pro-football-reference.com/leaders/pass_cmp_career.htm|title=Pro Football Reference&nbsp;<U+2013> Career Passes Completed Leaders|publisher=pro-football-reference.com|author=Drinen, Doug|accessdate=2007-12-21}}</ref>
* [[List of National Football League passing yardage leaders|Passing Yards]]: 53,187 (3rd)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pro-football-reference.com/leaders/pass_yds_career.htm|title=Pro Football Reference&nbsp;<U+2013> Career Passing Yards Leaders|publisher=pro-football-reference.com|author=Drinen, Doug|accessdate=2007-12-21}}</ref>
* [[NFL career passer rating leaders|Passer Rating]]: 95.1 (4th)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pro-football-reference.com/leaders/pass_rating_career.htm|title=Career Passer Rating Leaders|publisher=pro-football-reference.com|author=Drinen, Doug|accessdate=2007-12-28}}</ref>
* Passing Yards per Game: 263.3 (1st)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pro-football-reference.com/leaders/pass_yds_per_g_career.htm|title=Career Passing Yards per Game Leaders|publisher=pro-football-reference.com|author=Drinen, Doug|accessdate=2007-12-28}}</ref>
* Completion Percentage: 64.8% (5th)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pro-football-reference.com/leaders/pass_cmp_perc_career.htm|title=Career Pass Completion % Leaders|publisher=pro-football-reference.com|author=Drinen, Doug|accessdate=2007-12-28}}</ref>

(Updated November 22, 2010)

